% my-clamp: value min max my-clamp
3 1 10 my-clamp =               % 3  (in range)
15 1 10 my-clamp =              % 10 (clamped to max)
-5 1 10 my-clamp =              % 1  (clamped to min)
1 1 10 my-clamp =               % 1  (at lower bound)
10 1 10 my-clamp =              % 10 (at upper bound)

